short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Check out who has the pull requests, and who should have pull requests.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Harbor Master helps you ship product by knowing who is available to work on your pull requests.
With it, you will:
- See the breakdown on who is assigned to what and help your team run more efficiently.
- Know if you have pull requests to review.
- Know who to assign to review yours.
